title: IHME Increases Coronavirus Death Projections by 9%: Biggest Upticks in NY, MA, PA, GA
description: The Institute of Health Metrics and Evaluation (IHME) released an update to its model on Tuesday that increases the number of projected deaths from coronavirus in the United States to 65,976, up nine percent from the April 17 update projection of 60,308.
